Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)\pos(636,626)}Third Galactic Empire, Year 214
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing but an archaic weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To have fought the Royal Guard to a standstill for 40 stunde,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you Golden Seven live up to your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Condemnation Mirage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:00:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This this—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after two hundred years, a promise is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe there were more of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you should show some more backbone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, these will prove to be invaluable firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Student Council will take charge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right to tell us what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-President, go fetch the Student Council Property stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you touch the Valvraves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chosen by vote to represent the entire student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He might hate competition and stuff, but this is the one area where he's bullheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When Haruto gets like this, he won't listen to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him really well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One time, we ran away from home together, and he—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell them about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's a cute story!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you would think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, no one knows these robots better than Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should let him decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't get his way all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I cast my vote with her proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Democracy in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to vote, put it before the entire—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.59,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check these over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will get into them until after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, teachers are responsible for the safety of their students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because when you get like that, you always have a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That completes my mission from captain Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it's combat training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,Next! Who's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to take his mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder was dying to pilot a Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pilot one, you stop being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't tell anyone that you found those Valvraves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of things that I was able to protect, thanks to it, but I'm scared of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I get the feeling that I turned into an animal, and I'm always afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...that this indestructible body is someone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that maybe I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...really dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a human being, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Aina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they do what Sashinami says?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you were right, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it'd normally be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Satomi? For a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This's totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What just— Why did—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother is bugging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's the salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks like it could turn you into a frog...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got tons of veggies, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that rich aroma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thanks, but I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I boiled the heck out of those veggies, so you don't have to worry about chok—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures, since it was cooked by a girl whose appearance is deceiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you complimenting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest I can give.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you could cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miss Rukino. For helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate being in someone's debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheering me on. Earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, that was fun! Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'd call it "fun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite good, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, your name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ham-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is a Dorssian soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've written out the future of your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Plan Regarding the Military Development and Territorial Expansion of New JIOR"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pilot Selection Tests"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Establishment of Alliance With ARUS"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Implementation of Total Military Conscription"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to turn us into a military state?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is this country's only means of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Negotiations have broken down, huh? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The alarm isn't going off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Citizens of New JIOR.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This country is now under the control of L-elf Karlstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All citizens are hereby subject to mandatory conscription.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will give your lives to pave the way for the growth of the state.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's launched a coup d'etat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kyuma Inuzuka, it isn't safe to stand there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have set traps throughout the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you do not wish to die, I suggest that you remain where you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Thunder, the gang leader of Sakimori Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.63,Alt,,0,0,0,,No way, this is the third floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all about guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate a man's fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're here, I take it that means there aren't any traps in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't anticipate this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you some payback from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit trying to act so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no need to anticipate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,End of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand girls at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she was suddenly so eager to help Shoko with the cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was to thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind of a stickler for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember one other time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking another picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they say that guy is single now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in there and make your move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For your knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who can thank people is a good person at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you became a Kamitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamitsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, from the biting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like that. I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've been touched by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By God?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're indestructible, can possess people, and can pilot that amazing robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think only God could be behind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamitsuki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it. It's way better than "monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Citizens of New JIOR.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This country is now under the control of L-elf Karistein.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokishima Haruto, report to classroom 2-B immediately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will have you operate your Valvrave as the core of our national defense force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've known better.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect him to go up against the entire school by himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I blow your brains out, I suspect that even you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was me from 15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A recording, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're this gullible, you'll never be able to protect those precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Precious to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall telling you it was a phantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A world without conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A-drei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with one eye, I'd recognize you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I anticipated combat in here, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me to believe that you would turn traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me? For shooting out your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to be my right hand man one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One eye is a small price to pay for the ultimate hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of becoming anyone's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found a right hand of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the school free...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never going to be your soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the school free...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This country needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to your senses, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you alive in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prof. Kibukawa, how did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a physics teacher, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep them safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You, a fool who can't even calculate properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf! Come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that get in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Q-vier! I've left the gate open!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Capture him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to capture him, Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a sentimental softy, Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna blow him to hell in my Carmilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's where you are, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running, he's running!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The great L-elf is running!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Traitors deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't, we're gonna get a nasty scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your upbringing was noble to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Skewers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kicked out the door, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch to Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, take up siege formation and commence attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a force waiting outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tokishima Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm gonna show you some new steps I worked up just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's come out... H-neun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know, I know, stick to the plan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're running?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants a one-on-one fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These things are—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Adhesive electromagnetic boomerangs created as a peacekeeping measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These will keep you from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's keeping Tokishima Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I amputate the leg?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that would impede his ability to pilot the Valvrave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no time to remove this beam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The conclusion I'm led to is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The temperature is climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your leg has been skewed by a steel beam, you can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't pilot my Valvrave,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you have no use for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Use my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordering me around again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee that my body will activate the Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, there is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seriously expect me to trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the choice with the best chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit IV's radiant heat is at 80% capacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die, you'll die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've factored in that risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All wrapped up and ready to take home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I had!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruto, watch out for these boomerang things!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Adhesive electromagnetic boomerangs"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as he predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Only target the unit that launches the boomerangs," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,H-neun! Crossfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinpoint accuracy like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand-to-hand combat, huh? With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fall back, H-neun! Gain distance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"H-neun tends to choose hahd-to-hand combat against opponents who get close."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that guy, a prophet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Objective is not to defeat the target, but rather to destroy the launcher."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-neun, are you all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, I got careless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That wasn't the result of carelessness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They have L-elf on their side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew, he really was a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our first plan has hit a roadblock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll fall back and come up with a new one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's body-jacked someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better take you somewhere before somebody sees you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were here—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We pulled through somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this mean, I'm invincible if I work with you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Licht... "Light"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Princess of Light".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will expose the truth of the world.
